results.name: Number of disconnected regular simple graphs on n vertices with girth at least 7.
link: Jason Kimberley, Index of sequences counting disconnected k-regular simple graphs with girth at least g
xref: Disconnected regular graphs with girth at least g: A068932 (g=3), A185214 (g=4), A185215 (g=5), A185216 (g=6), this sequence (g=7).
Disconnected k-regular simple graphs with girth at least 7: this sequence (all k), A185207 (triangle); A185227 (k=2), A185237 (k=3).
